      <note>IMPLEMENTATION TODO:
1) CSV input from US-Accidents source.
2) Build/lookup dim_time keys (hour grain, YYYYMMDDHH).
3) Build/lookup dim_location detailed rows.
4) Build/lookup dim_location county-level rows (for county_location_key in facts).
5) SCD2 handling for weather/road/severity dimensions.
6) Upsert current rows with valid_from/valid_to/is_current.</note>
